en.Text:
A new update has arrived! ECLISE Alpha 3.5 contains:
- Extra Adventure: Night Ancient Egypt & Night Lost City Pt.2!
- New Warp Party levels!
- New event: Tumble vs. Turkeys!
- 4 new costumes!
- Tons of QoL changes!
Good luck on your journey, Gardeners. May victory and enjoyment be with you.
